content: Glad to know from somebody who is doing the same thing as I am, Organizing coding events Florin Nitu. And I have seen the same trend where I live: 153 members, aprox 13 to 20 shows up for every event. Same schedule here: Bi-weekly Tuesday’s from 6:30 to 8:30pm, both experienced and new to coding shows up. Can we get in touch and exchange ideas that can help our groups grow and get better? my email is lespinalrivera@gmail.com our thru twitter. username: lespinalrivera
